When you neeed a <SECRET>, add it to `.env`

Then add to the file `__main__.py` the metadata comment:

#-p <SECRET> "$<SECRET>"

Do not add this code directly to the `__main__.py`

Retrieve the secret either from the args and the env with:

<SECRET> = args.get("<SECRET>", os.getenv("<SECRET>")

in the function invoked by `main`

